  249\t    .createQueryBuilder("m")\n   250\t    .where("m.conversation_id IN (:
...ids)", { ids: conversationIds })\n   251\t    .getMany();\n   252\t  ```\n   
253\t\n   254\t- **陷阱 7**：**唯一索引与幂等去重查询语义不一致**。若数据库唯一
